OL,5, Controversial Cardinal George Pell     
OL,6, wrote an anonymous memo criticising the
OL,7, Pope's leadership as a "catastrophe",  
OL,8, says the journalist who released it.   
OL,10,FThe Australian cardinal, who died on   
OL,11,FTuesday aged 81, was one of Pope       
OL,12,FFrancis' top aides until he stepped    
OL,13,Fdown to face child sex abuse charges.  
OL,15,FThe memo was published on a Vatican    
OL,16,Fblog site under a pseudonym last year. 
OL,18,FIt detailed what the author deemed were
OL,19,Ffailures of the current Pope and a list
OL,20,Fof priorities for choosing the next.   
